snippet.title: Super Mega Zero Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Miss Undefined has been whisked away by the dastardly Kill Screen. Go from Zero to Hero in this fast-paced platformer, chasing time, the high score, and eventually the Kill Screen itself.

Super Mega Zero is jumping on to Nintendo Switch and PC on April 21st, 2022.

Wishlist on Steam Now - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1581880/Super_Mega_Zero/
Pre-Order On Nintendo Switch Now - https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/super-mega-zero-switch/
